EVERYTHING IS TERRIBLE! THE RISE & FALL OF GOD [2013] DVD Rip

In our short time on this planet, Spectacle has played host to a veritable Who's Who of Who On Earth? type guests - bodybuilding computer hackers, stop-motion royalty, literal Oscar winners, sonic gurus, political revolutionaries, etc. - and now, we can add one more to that list as we welcome the found footage titans of EVERYTHING IS TERRIBLE! for the New York premiere of their cut-and-paste sermon THE RISE AND FALL OF GOD!

DVD rip using HandBrake

720x480, 4:3 strict anamorphic aspect ratio
H.264 video, 30 FPS, constant quality RF 25
AAC audio, 160 kbps, 48kHz

This DVD has no menus and all video names were found online. Bonus videos 1-5 were presented as one title without chapter markers. I have split the video myself. Bonus video 6 was a separate title.

This is one of at least 4 bonus DVDs EIT! has produced, available for a limited time in 2013. The other 3 bonus DVDs, none of which I have, are:
1) EIT HOLIDAY SPECIAL (2011 version)
2) 2 MINUTE MOVIES compilation
3) 2 HOT 4 DA NET compilation of videos banned from YouTube
